- Update to 2.5.1:
  * fcft_set_scaling_filter now applies to color bitmap fonts only,
    ie emoji fonts.
  * Fixed incorrect value of FCFT_SCALING_FILTER_CUBIC constant.
  * Fixed pixman errors and program freezes when scaling bitmap fonts to
    very small sizes.

